oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Grass silage in diets for organic growingfinishing pigs
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Bikker, P.
Binnendijk, G.P.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Feeding and growth
Pigs
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The supply of a mixed ration of grass silage and concentrate to growing-finishing pigs reduced the growth performance and feed utilisation. Further improvements of the feeding system would be required to substantially reduce the feed costs.
oai_dc:dc.dc:identifier: Bikker, P. and Binnendijk, G.P. (2012) Grass silage in diets for organic growingfinishing pigs. .
